{"word":"καλύπτω","slug":"καλύπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαλύπτω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>ϰαλιά</el> ‘hut’] <b>cover, conceal</b> in physical sense of concealing <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> view <b><a href='B:470 8:24'>Mt 8:24</a></b> (a boat hidden from view); <b><a href='B:490 8:16'>Lk 8:16</a>; <a href='B:490 23:30'>23:30</a>.</b> In imagery: <b><a href='B:470 10:26'>Mt 10:26</a>;</b> covering with a veil <b><a href='B:490 24:32'>Lk 24:32</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:540 4:3'>2 Cor 4:3</a>; <a href='B:660 5:20'>Js 5:20</a>; <a href='B:670 4:8'>1 Pt 4:8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κάλυμμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καλῶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}